values:
&nbsp;Lately I haven't been doing good. My arm is feeling alittle better since it is getting warmer. My leg is still doing really bad. I barely can walk again. I am in a wheel chair when going out. I can manage to walk room to room. I have been taking alot of naps. Yesturday my mom, Katie, Jordyn and I went to khols, Target, and went out to lunch to pizza hut by the time we were done I was&nbsp;so exhausted that when I got home I passed out in my clothes and everything I was wearing. I am just trying to hang in there till my pain management appointment on the 14th.&nbsp;

I went last saturday to retake my written test and I PASSED. So this passed Tuesday and Wednesday I went and drove 2 hours behind the wheel each day so I did 4 hours, I only have 2 more hours and I will get my permit! YEAH!

I'll update more later. Love, Ashley

&nbsp;I started the methadone Friday. It is making me dizzy, my heart race,&nbsp; me tired, and very itchy. It is helping my side just a tiny bit. I guess that is better than nothing so far.&nbsp; Hopefully when he ups it, It will take more pain away.

One day this week I go to&nbsp;take my written test for my permit. YEAH.&nbsp;

Thats all for now i'll update more later. Love, Ashley&nbsp;
